text: Abderrahmane Farès (; ALA-LC: ʿAbd ar-Raḥman Fāris; ; January 30, 1911 – May 13, 1991) was the Chairman of the Provisional Executive of Algeria from 13 April 1962 to 20 September 1962. ==References== Category:1911 births Category:1991 deaths Category:Presidents of Algeria
title: Abderrahmane Farès
